title: LSI MegaRAID: State of Virtual Drives (via StorCLI)
agents: windows
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the state of the virtual drives of an LSI
 MegaRAID controller. The corresponding agent plugin uses the
 {storcli64.exe} utility, provided its location has been correctly
 entered in the script.

item:
 The controller number and the ID of the virtual drive.

inventory:
 One service is created for each found virtual drive on each controller.
